# JNLOP Core Context

This is the **JNLOP MVP** greenfield Turborepo for JNIC church operations.

## Before coding

1. Read `AGENTS.md`
2. Read `context/progress-tracker.md` for current phase
3. Read the relevant `context/feature-specs/` file for the active epic

## Non-negotiables

- RBAC enforced in NestJS guards — never UI-only
- Active phase gating in `context/mvp-roadmap.md` — do not skip ahead
- Shared enums in `packages/types` — no duplication
- JNIC brand tokens from `context/ui-context.md` — no hardcoded hex
- `jubilee-nation` is UX reference only — do not import its code

## Role model

`LEAD_PASTOR` > `ADMIN` > `STATE_PASTOR` > `ZONAL_PASTOR` > `BRANCH_PASTOR` > `ADMIN_STAFF`

Admin and HQ Admin are the same `ADMIN` role.

## After each feature unit

Update `context/progress-tracker.md`.
